1. *Bacite* loptu preko ograde. (Throw* the ball over the fence.)
2. Molim vas da mi *bacite* papir za zapisivanje. (Please, *pass* me a piece of paper for taking notes.)
3. *Bacila* je smeće u kontejner. (She *threw away* the trash in the dumpster.)
4. *Bacite* pogled na ovu sliku. (Take a *look* at this picture.)
5. Moramo *baciti* sve stare stvari iz kuće. (We need to *get rid of* all the old things from the house.)
6. *Bacili* smo novčić da odlučimo ko će prvi baciti kocku. (We *tossed* a coin to decide who would roll the dice first.)
7. *Bacite* se na posao da završimo na vreme. (Let's *get down* to work to finish on time.)
8. Neću *baciti* novac na nešto što mi nije potrebno. (I won't *waste* money on something I don't need.)
9. Molim vas da *bacite* pogled na ove dokumente i proverite da li su ispravni. (Please, *take a look* at these documents and check if they are correct.)
10. Kada je čuo loše vesti, *bacio* je pogled u pod. (When he heard the bad news, he *lowered* his gaze.)